★Battery Saver: Search at the code level for high power usage apps, configure power-saving mode and disable apps that consume power without performance, extending the life of the battery by 30%.

★CPU Cooler: CPU Cooler provides an in-depth analysis of tens of thousands of Apps to lower CPU consumption, in order to prevent the phone from getting hot, and achieving smoother operation.

★Security: One-click to detect phone loopholes, malicious ads, and apps that maliciously steal private data round the clock.

★Wi-Fi Security: Smart scanning of surrounding Wi-Fi networks to ensure Wi-Fi security in a public environment.

★App Management: Smart management of application status conjoined with batch deletion and backup of Apps.

KeepClean is more reliable!

✔Service-oriented: focuses on resolving the compatibility issue of models and versions of Android phones, featuring better localization and compatibility.

✔Low consumption: stable operation and super-low usage of internal storage.

KeepClean is a technology-driven and customized acceleration app; it helps Android phones to solve such problems as cleaning up large junk documents, putting a stop to apps from continually restarting while performing background processes, having your CPU being bogged down, and even overheating. KeepClean is focused on keeping your device functioning as if it were new!

✨HIGHLIGHTS OF KEEPCLEAN:

★Junk Clean: The app is able to clean the unwanted cache by using big data analysis., one-click cleanup of app and system junk files to completely free up space on device.

★Speed up: Smart cleanup provides the ability to free up memory and improve the phones operating speed.

★Battery Saver: Locates and disables inactive high power consumption apps. Check battery status and activate various power-saving features with a single tap. Prolongs standby duration of up to 70% and optimizes the battery health and usage.

★CPU Cooler: CPU Cooler provides an in-depth analysis of tens of thousands of Apps to lower CPU consumption, in order to prevent the phone from getting hot, and achieving smoother operation.

★Security: One-click to detect phone loopholes, malicious ads, and apps that maliciously steal private data round the clock.

★Wi-Fi Security: Smart scanning of surrounding Wi-Fi networks to ensure Wi-Fi security in a public environment.

★Special cleanup for Social Apps: In-depth checking of pictures, audios, videos and other documents generated in running social apps, with the ability to remove useless documents and backup valuable documents.

★App Management: Smart management of application status conjoined with batch deletion and backup of Apps.

KeepClean is more reliable!

✔Service-oriented: focuses on resolving the compatibility issue of models and versions of Android phones, featuring better localization and compatibility.

✔Technology-driven: forged by a professional technical team, equipped with the stronger capability of low-layer technology.

✔Low consumption: stable operation and super-low usage of internal storage.

✔Space-saving: small-size installation package that saves space for the mobile phone.
descriptionShort: A more compatible cleaner for Android.

creator: APPS INNOVA
descriptionHtml:
KeepClean is the most reliable all-in-one Android device optimization and free antivirus application in the world that integrates the functions of Phone Cleaner, RAM Optimizer, Battery Saver, and more for optimum performance and security.

Over 50,000,000 people have installed KeepClean to optimize and protect their Android devices. Join now to access the following features for free.

🆑Junk Cleanup: Perform accurate analysis of apps’ cache and junk files. Clean up apps’ and system’s junk files with one tap to free up storage.

🚀Phone Speedup: Speed up your phone’s performance by thoroughly freeing up the phone’s RAM.

🔋Battery Saver: Detect and disable redundant power-consuming apps to extend standby duration by up to 70%. Also supports various power-saving modes.

⚡Quick Charging: Increase your phone’s charging speed and prolong its battery life by closing unused background apps when charging.

📶Wi-Fi Security: Scan for unauthorized WiFi connections to maximize your phone’s security.

❄CPU Cooling: Perform detailed analysis of thousands of apps to reduce the CPU consumption and prevent device overheating.

🔐Traceless Browsing: Private web browser that safeguards your browsing history and protects your privacy.

📂Social Media App: Perform detailed scans of images, videos, and audio files generated by social media apps, removing useless files while backing up necessary ones.

🎮Game Booster: Close unused background apps to free up RAM and boost your phone’s performance.

✔Software Management: Efficiently manage apps’ statuses by carrying out batch deletion and backup of apps.

Premium Features:

❌No Ads: Experience KeepClean without the disruption of ads.

💪VIP Support: Receive prompt responses to your inquiries by contacting KeepClean directly from the app.

⏰Automatic Cleanup: Clean up junk files at fixed intervals to speed up your phone.

♻Image & Video Recovery: Recover deleted photos and videos.

🔏Privacy Vault: Encrypt and hide your private photos, videos, etc.

📸Intruder Snaps: Capture snapshots when someone tries to unlock your phone with an incorrect PIN, pattern, or password.

🆑Similar Photo Cleanup: Scan & automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage.

KeepClean NOTES:
None of the personal data such as username or email address proceeds.
All information will be kept secure and not shared with the 3rd party according to Privacy and Cookies Policy.

KeepClean is the most reliable all-in-one Android device optimization and free antivirus application in the world that integrates the functions of Phone Cleaner, RAM Optimizer, Antivirus, Battery Saver, and more for optimum performance and security.

Over 50,000,000 people have installed KeepClean to optimize and protect their Android devices. Join now to access the following features for free.

🆑Junk Cleanup: Perform accurate analysis of apps’ cache and junk files. Clean up apps’ and system’s junk files with one tap to free up storage.

🚀Phone Speedup: Speed up your phone’s performance by thoroughly freeing up the phone’s RAM.

🔋Battery Saver: Detect and disable redundant power-consuming apps to extend standby duration by up to 70%. Also supports various power-saving modes.

⚡Quick Charging: Increase your phone’s charging speed and prolong its battery life by closing unused background apps when charging.

🛡Antivirus Security: Protect your privacy by receiving alerts when spyware or adware programs are downloaded to your device. Secure your device against phishing attacks from emails and malicious websites.

📶Wi-Fi Security: Scan for unauthorized WiFi connections to maximize your phone’s security.

❄CPU Cooling: Perform detailed analysis of thousands of apps to reduce the CPU consumption and prevent device overheating.

🔐Traceless Browsing: Private web browser that safeguards your browsing history and protects your privacy.

📂Social Media App: Perform detailed scans of images, videos, and audio files generated by social media apps, removing useless files while backing up necessary ones.

🎮Game Booster: Close unused background apps to free up RAM and boost your phone’s performance.

✔Software Management: Efficiently manage apps’ statuses by carrying out batch deletion and backup of apps.

Premium Features:

❌No Ads: Experience KeepClean without the disruption of ads.

💪VIP Support: Receive prompt responses to your inquiries by contacting KeepClean directly from the app.

⏰Automatic Cleanup: Clean up junk files at fixed intervals to speed up your phone.

♻Image & Video Recovery: Recover deleted photos and videos.

🔏Privacy Vault: Encrypt and hide your private photos, videos, etc.

📸Intruder Snaps: Capture snapshots when someone tries to unlock your phone with an incorrect PIN, pattern, or password.

🆑Similar Photo Cleanup: Scan & automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage.

KeepClean NOTES:
None of the personal data such as username or email address proceeds.
All information will be kept secure and not shared with the 3rd party according to Privacy and Cookies Policy.

title: KeepClean: Cleaner, Antivirus

creator: APPS INNOVA
descriptionHtml:
KeepClean is all-in-one Android device optimization and antivirus application that integrates the functions of Phone Cleaner, RAM Optimizer, Antivirus, Battery Saver, and more for optimum performance and security.

Over 100,000,000 people have installed KeepClean to optimize and protect their Android devices. Join now to access the following features for free.

🆑Junk Cleanup: Perform accurate analysis of apps’ cache and junk files. Clean up apps’ and system’s junk files with one tap to free up storage.

🚀Phone Speedup: Speed up your phone’s performance by thoroughly freeing up the phone’s RAM.

🔋Battery Saver: Detect and disable redundant power-consuming apps to extend standby duration by up to 70%. Also supports various power-saving modes.

🛡Antivirus Security: Provide professional service to scan and remove all kinds of viruses and trojans to protect your phone which is powered by Kaspersky.

❄CPU Cooling: Perform detailed analysis of thousands of apps to reduce the CPU consumption and prevent device overheating.

🎮Game Booster: Close unused background apps to free up RAM and boost your phone’s performance.

📸Similar Photo Cleanup: Scan & automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage.

📶Wi-Fi Security: Scan for unauthorized WiFi connections to maximize your phone’s security.

KeepClean NOTES:
None of the personal data such as username or email address proceeds.
All information will be kept secure and not shared with the 3rd party according to Privacy and Cookies Policy.

descriptionHtml:
KeepClean is all-in-one Android device optimization and antivirus application that integrates the functions of Phone Cleaner, RAM Optimizer, Antivirus, Battery Saver, and more for optimum performance and security.

🔋Battery Saver: Detect and disable redundant power-consuming apps to extend standby duration by up to 70%. Also supports various power-saving modes.

📸Similar Photo Cleanup: Scan & automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage.

📶Wi-Fi Security: Scan for unauthorized WiFi connections to maximize your phone’s security.

KeepClean NOTES:
None of the personal data such as username or email address proceeds.
